data.description: Come and see this beautiful 3 BEDROOM, 2.5 BATH home in popular Kingstree. Great floorplan featuring an OPEN layout w/ a spacious living room that flows right into the large kitchen w/ granite countertops and pantry. Easy maintenance backyard with PRIVACY FENCE on CORNER LOT. Large primary suite on upper level features double closets, vaulted ceilings and an ensuite bath w/ garden tub. Two additional bedrooms separated by the second full-bath complete the upper level. Kingstree is a great amenity-rich community w/ its own community clubhouse, pool, playground, sidewalks and walking trail. The community is conveniently located within minutes to shopping, grocers and restaurants.
